{"tid":1516872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[要人要人要人] 務求用最短時間將所有聯署達標！搵1000位組長先！","createTime":"2019-08-29T17:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T19:07:20.000Z","uid":245968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"784cad1903bdf7842aeea0b7f4767ed4623a846b","tid":1516872,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:09:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，實在太多聯署要簽<br />\n成日都唔夠數，又唔知簽咗未<br />\n<br />\n咁不如直接開group<br />\n組長負責send聯署link<br />\n其他人只需簽名後已讀不回，以免混亂<br />\n<br />\n「組長group」 1組 1000人 <br />\n負責交流整合聯署link<br />\n<br />\n「簽名group」 1000組 每組100人<br />\n組長自組100人group，send link比人簽<br />\n最好搵身邊朋友，唔好搵陌生人<br />\n<br />\n如果成功，應該唔使一日就夠數<br />\n其他途徑繼續宣傳，多多益善<br />\n<br />\n有一個白色恐怖風險<br />\n入咗一隻鬼就出賣晒咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想手足討論下方法可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cc643825c4d46c2553fcd8cec4fedad6150553","tid":1516872,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:10:57.000Z","msg":"有Twitter既入黎報數！Twitter要人! Twitter要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輸撚硬啦，無人做實事，文宣組幫咗你做文宣做得咁辛苦 你肯唔肯開個twitter 幫佢地？"},{"pid":"b18f0f839954d54f5737dde938f7786b606f2d6b","tid":1516872,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f93b5380c39408ed6748e257cb47b3eee285bc","tid":1516872,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i